		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p>This is a list of famous <a href="/wiki/Hutu" title="Hutu">Hutus</a> who have Wikipedia biographies which include mention of Hutu identity.
</p>
